g.text: EditJobOpeningUI Sequence Diagram (SSD) - Edit a Job Opening
Asks to edit a job opening
Chooses a job opening to edit
[until the Customer Manager is satisfied with the changes]
Shows list of job opening attributes
Attributes are: Title or function, Contract Type, Mode, Address,
Number of vacancies, Description and Requirement Specification
depending on the phase that the recruitment process is in.
Shows current value of chosen attribute and asks for new value
Provides new value for chosen attribute
[Interview Initial Date exists and is updated]
[Interview Final Date exists and is updated]
Informs success or failure of update
